the SF Police homicide detective, Inspector Toschi, taunting
him. Some were encrypted.

The Zodiac claimed that his victims would become his slaves
in the hereafter.

One time he particularly terrified the Bay Area. He threatened
to "pick off the kiddies as they come bounding off the school
bus."

